  "texts": [
    "It is also essential to establish standardized protocols for sensory evaluation to improve reproducibility and comparability across studies.",
    "Ethical issues must be addressed as well, especially those related to consumer privacy, data transparency, and the responsible use of AI in shaping taste and odor preferences.",
    "Progress in these areas will benefit from interdisciplinary collaboration that brings together AI developers, sensory scientists, food technologists, and ethicists.",
    "By fostering this collaboration, the field can move toward more reliable, transparent, and inclusive applications of AI, ultimately contributing to innovations that improve product quality and enhance the everyday experiences of consumers."
